*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Domain: ZLL_REQUEST_STATUS
*& Description: Emergency Request Status Domain for LifeLink
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*
* Domain Name  : ZLL_REQUEST_STATUS
* Data Type    : CHAR
* Length       : 10
* Output Length: 10
*
* Fixed Values:
* Value      | Short Description
* -----------|------------------
* PENDING    | Pending Approval
* APPROVED   | Approved
* REJECTED   | Rejected
* COMPLETED  | Completed
* CANCELLED  | Cancelled
*
* Usage: Used in ZLL_EMRG_REQ table for request workflow status
